{"tid":355321,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"想知連登仔心目中嘅肥婆指標","createTime":"2017-08-11T07:57:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-11T09:10:40.000Z","uid":125873,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a86685df8f3f811530cda1a508c4fc84fae97c84","tid":355321,"uid":125873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T07:57:36.000Z","msg":"啫係BMI幾多先會叫佢肥婆？<br />\n我意思係大約啦 <br />\n因為見你地個個post都唔同嘅<br />\n有啲少肥算正常身型又肥婆 有啲極度癡肥又肥婆 <br />\n所以想知身邊嘅朋友會唔會成為你地眼中嘅死肥婆，然後有日俾人推上連登<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n一係大家post張你地覺得最瘦嘅肥婆身型上嚟 啫係邊到起跳係就肥婆<br />\n <br />\n利申 我唔係肥婆 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/11/155727_4e1af642508476c81542b9067db52b1c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F11%2F155727_4e1af642508476c81542b9067db52b1c.jpg&h=3ddc73fd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/11/155727_3630944b6dbc829d0913f9c683d1283d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F11%2F155727_3630944b6dbc829d0913f9c683d1283d.jpg&h=2cb44e62&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ce8d47d9da7d6b6aa47ca37f2bda469e1af0850f","tid":355321,"uid":134997,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T08:03:46.000Z","msg":"我"},{"pid":"b22a5bf20bd7221b76c9a878587e00c5ca29d222","tid":355321,"uid":125873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T08:07:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我</blockquote><br />\n肥佬扮咩肥婆先"},{"pid":"daaa75a640864e3b4cbebf69f159dbfb55e6c639","tid":355321,"uid":129054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T08:21:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f1e4b856fb4d6536a32bb6d95deadd94bc56503c","tid":355321,"uid":48830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T08:23:32.000Z","msg":"睇身型㗎嘛 講BMI點講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgm